pma:database.name: overwatch_skins
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `category` ( `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `icon_url` text NOT NULL, `display_ow1_order` int DEFAULT NULL, `display_ow2_order` int DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), KEY `display_ow1` (`display_ow1_order`), KEY `display_ow2` (`display_ow2_order`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=19 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `hero` ( `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(30) NOT NULL, `role` enum('tank','damage','support') NOT NULL, `release_date` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '2016-05-24', `portrait_url` text NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=45 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `season` ( `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `start_date` date NOT NULL, `end_date` date NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=20 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `skin` ( `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `id_hero` int NOT NULL, `id_category` int NOT NULL, `id_season` int DEFAULT NULL, `year` int DEFAULT NULL, `image_url` text NOT NULL, `rarity` enum('common','rare','epic','legendary','mythic') NOT NULL, `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `id_category_secondary` int DEFAULT NULL, `id_condition` int DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), UNIQUE KEY `id_hero_2` (`id_hero`,`name`), KEY `id_category` (`id_category`), KEY `id_season` (`id_season`), KEY `id_hero` (`id_hero`), KEY `id_category_secondary` (`id_category_secondary`), KEY `id_condition` (`id_condition`), CONSTRAINT `skin_category` FOREIGN KEY (`id_category`) REFERENCES `category` (`id`) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `skin_category_secondary` FOREIGN KEY (`id_category_secondary`) REFERENCES `category` (`id`) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `skin_condition` FOREIGN KEY (`id_condition`) REFERENCES `condition_special` (`id`) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `skin_hero` FOREIGN KEY (`id_hero`) REFERENCES `hero` (`id`) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `skin_season` FOREIGN KEY (`id_season`) REFERENCES `season` (`id`) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1718 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;
